    <description>Intracoronary provocation of coronary spasm with acetylcholine in augmented dosages of 2 µg, 20 µg, 100 µg and 200 µg non-selectively in the LCA as well as 80 µg in the RCA. During the procedure, a 12 channel ECG will be recorded.</description>
